		<description><![CDATA[<p>For our seventh Student Spotlight, we chatted to Krystian Kopec, a bass player whose story with SBL began 18 months ago. Throughout the year, we’ll be catching up with a diverse set of breaking and established talent to air their...</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com/notes/sbl-student-spotlight-krystian-kopec.html">SBL Student Spotlight &#8211; Krystian Kopec</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.scottsbasslessons.com">Online Bass Lessons</a>.</p>
